## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **eltrombopag Promacta 2008** = first FDA TPO-RA — chronic ITP 의 만성 paradigm 시작. small-molecule oral + non-peptide TPO-mimetic. quantum-VQE 의 MPL extracellular pocket fit.
2. **romiplostim Nplate 2008** = second TPO-RA + Fc-peptide fusion — SC weekly. peptide-mimetic 의 TPO-R agonist. quantum-VQE 의 peptide-receptor scaffold fit.
3. **avatrombopag Doptelet 2018 + lusutrombopag Mulpleta 2018** = pre-procedural ITP + CLD. third + fourth TPO-RA. 만성 chronic ITP 영역 확대.
4. **fostamatinib Tavalisse 2018** = first FDA Syk inhibitor — refractory chronic ITP. R406 active metabolite. quantum-VQE 의 Syk ATP-pocket fit.
5. **rilzabrutinib Phase 3 LUNA-3 (Sanofi)** = reversible covalent BTK inhibitor — chronic ITP. ibrutinib 류와 distinct kinetics. quantum-VQE 의 BTK reversible covalent dynamics fit.
6. **efgartigimod Vyvgart 2021 + nipocalimab Imaavy 2024 (MG approval, ITP research)** = FcRn antagonist class — IgG-lowering. ITP autoantibody-mediated platelet destruction 직접 표적. cross-myasthenia_specific paradigm transfer.
7. **sutimlimab Enjaymo 2022** = first FDA classical-pathway C1q inhibitor — cold agglutinin disease. ITP + 만성 complement-mediated overlap research. cross-bone_marrow_failure PNH C5 distinct.
8. **splenectomy 만성 표준 + rituximab 2차** = surgical + immunosuppressive 표준. 신규 small-molecule 가 splenectomy 회피 paradigm 진행.
9. **K-ITP 식약처 framework + 산정특례** = eltrombopag + romiplostim + fostamatinib 한국 급여 기준. 만성 chronic ITP 환자 long-term cost burden.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, ITP 임상 의미 한정. TPO-RA long-term safety (eltrombopag 만성 hepatotoxicity + bone marrow reticulin 만성) 양자 modeling 한계.

